GAMEPLAY: The CT's Win If They Rescue Hostage. The Terrorist Win If They Sucessfully Detonate The Bomb, CT's Will Win, If They Rescue Hostages, Before Bomb Goes Off, Even If Bomb Has Been Planted, By Terrorist, Also CT's Win If Clock Runs Out, And Terrorist Don't Succesfully Detonate The Bomb Within Time Limit. CT's Can Also Defuse The Bomb To Win. 


                 HOSTAGE/BOMB MAP.

THE STORY BEHIND THE MAP THE TERRORIST HAVE CATPURE THE OPERATIVES, AND THERE ASSESTS VIA LOTS OF MONEY FOUND ON PALLETS IN THE MAP, THE TERRORIST HAVE WIRED THE MONEY WITH BOMBS, AND THE TERRORIST HAVE ALSO WIRED THE HOSTAGE WITH THE BOMBS, THE TERRORIST HAVE TO STRATEGICALLY DETONATE THE LAST BOMB, AND THE REST OF THE BOMBS WILL REMOTRLY DETONATE, WITH THE MAIN BOMB. THE TERRORIST HAVE RANSCACKED THE ZONE ENTRANCE AND KILLED ALL BUT A MEDIC,AND 1 COP WHO IS AT THE SCENCE, WHEN THE CT'S ARRIVE THEY ARE UPDATED WITH RECON BY THE COP, THAT IS LOCATED IN THE GYM, THE TERRORIST ARE HOLDING THE OPERATIVES HOSTAGE,THE TERRORIST HAVE WIRED THE OPERATIVES WITH BOMBS THAT WILL BLOW UP WHEN THE MAIN BOMB DETONATES, THE TERRORIST ARE ARMED AND HEAVLY AND DANGEROUS. THERE IS A MEDIC WAITING IN HOSTAGE RESCUE WAITING TO DEBUG THE HOSTAGES, SO THE DON'T EXPLOID WHEN THE MAIN BOMB GOES OFF!, THE CT'S ONLY MISSION IS TO GET IN THERE, AND GET THE HOSTAGE DUBUG BY THE MEDIC, OR STOP THE TERRORIST FROM DETONATING THE BOMB, OR KILL ALL TERRORIST.

I RECOMMEND "1368 X 768" Video Card Settings, For This Map, It Really Brings Out The Lighting Especially The Lights You Can Turn Off, Also Less Lag, And I personal Think It Looks Better, 1600 x 900 Has More Shaders It Seems, Differnet Look to it.
